reviewText: I watched this for about 30 minutes before (yawn) turning it off).  My 25 year old said, "Why did you wait so long?".  This might be a movie tweens 10-12 might like, but I kept wondering why two girls were staying in a cabin with the other boys until I finally figured out they were boys.  Not a great movie at all.
summary: Not for adults or younger children, something the tweens might like
Title: Rainbow Tribe

reviewText: I have a teenager who has had a rough life due to the cercumstances in the family.  I can relate to these children and the movie gave me some ideas in handling some situations.
